### Test Course API - Base Response Format

@Course_HostAddress = http://localhost:5002

# Health Check
GET {{Course_HostAddress}}/ping

###

# Get All Courses - BaseListResponse<CourseDTO>
GET {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses

###

# Get Courses with Pagination - BaseListResponse<CourseDTO> with pagination info
GET {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses/paged?Page=1&Limit=5&SearchKey=

###

# Get Courses with Pagination and Search - BaseListResponse<CourseDTO>
GET {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses/paged?Page=1&Limit=3&SearchKey=Clean

###

# Get Courses Page 2 - BaseListResponse<CourseDTO>
GET {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses/paged?Page=2&Limit=5

###

# Get Course By ID - BaseResponse<CourseDTO> (Success)
GET {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###

# Get Course By ID - BaseResponse<CourseDTO> (Not Found)
GET {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000999

###

# Create Course - BaseResponse<CourseDTO>
POST {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Introduction to Clean Architecture",
  "description": "Learn the fundamentals of Clean Architecture in .NET",
  "instructor": "John Doe",
  "type": 0,
  "price": 99.99,
  "duration": 120
}

