###

# Update Course - BaseResponse<CourseDTO>
PUT {{Course_HostAddress}}/api/courses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Advanced Clean Architecture",
  "description": "Advanced concepts in Clean Architecture",
  "instructor": "Jane Smith",
